title: 이달의소녀탐구 #35 (LOONA TV #35)
summary:
2Jin are eatin’. This episode is edited to look like one giant meal, but actually
(based on the clothing changes) it takes place over several meals.
0:02 -- HeeJin: “What shall we do now?” HyunJin: “We should go eat some food!”
0:08 -- HyunJin, “It’s Ramen!” Showing off her Japanese speaking. “Ramen Desu Imida”
hah.
